ies one is closed for redevelopment and seven other operating assets and investments the retail properties include columbia regional building columbia maryland cottonwood square salt lake city utah downtown summerlin las vegas nevada landmark mall alexandria virginia outlet collection at riverwalk new orleans louisiana park west peoria arizona and the seaport district new york new york the companys multifamily portfolio consists of constellation millennium waterway apartments one lakes edge and the metropolitan downtown its hospitality portfolio consists of embassy suites at hughes landing the westin at the woodlands and the woodlands resort  conference center its other assets include kewalo basin harbor the woodlands parking garages and woodlands sarofimstrategic developmentsas of december   the companys strategic developments segment included  development projects as of december   the company had  properties under construction its portfolio of projects include anaha creekside park apartments  fellowship drive ke kilohana one merriweather two merriweather allentowne american city building bridges at mint hill cottonwood mall kendall town center and west windsor » full overview of hhc company address howard hughes corp  noel rd fl dallas   tx    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation william ackman  grant herlitz  david weinreb  david oreilly  christopher curry  » more officers  directors howard hughes corp news briefwilliam ackman reports  pct stake in howard hughes corp jul   briefthe howard hughes corp announces pricing of addon offering of pct senior notes jun   briefthe howard hughes announces commencement of addon offering of  pct senior notes due  jun   ackman has a winner that is up  percent but will not name names may   ackman has a winner that is up  percent but will not name names may   » more hhc news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsreal estate development  operations the howard hughes corp  nysehhc  stock quo