esidential condominium developments the company was founded on november   and is headquartered in dallas tx see full profile analyst ratings sell under hold over buy number of ratings  full ratings ira sohn  conference everything you need to know may   at  pm et on benzingacom citi calls howard hughes underfollowed undervalued not fully understood initiates at buy may   at  am et on benzingacom tilson howard hughes and fannie mae are my  favorite stock ideas apr   at  pm et on benzingacom competitors name chg  market cap transcontinental realty investors inc  m new england realty associates lp un  m consolidatedtomoka land co  m competitor data provided by partner content trending tickers powered by dvax  s  ssti  mo  chtr  advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found video center learn morestoryful a division of news corp which owns marketwatch is a leading social media services company headquartered in dublin ireland storyful combines world class journalism with industryleading technology to discover verify and acquire original content and provide the ontheground sources news and media organizations need to tell the stories that matter to their audience hhc  investor relations   press releasesinvestors dashboard press releases filter by yearjulthe howard hughes corporation® announces secondquarter  earnings release and conference call dateshhc to host earnings call on august   dallasbusiness wirejul   the howard hughes corporation® nyse hhc announced today that it will release  secondquarter earnings on monday august   read full release  junthe howard hughes corporation® announces participation in the jmp securities  financial services and real estate conferencenew yorkbusiness wirejun   the howard hughes corporation® nyse hhc announced today that the company will be participating in the jmp securities  financial services and real estate conference on june  read full release  junthe howard hughes corporation® announces closing of addon offering o